  "rationale": "Repair note: replaced all content-block slots (source of the render KeyError 'body') with header blocks, feature-item runs, and flat primitive slots \u2014 no block in the page carries a 'body' slot. Order follows the brief's one-scroll narrative: an inverse hero bookend (the ONLY inverse surface and ONLY accent, sanctioned display-title-over-media with a media-over-media overlap + stagger), then an all-primary editorial run. About and Mission reuse/adapt the anchored-statement split (Mission adds a heavy 'MUSE' ghost word for the brief's outline typography). The gallery band reuses the full-bleed counter pattern with a static counter and marginal caption. Heritage adapts the feature grid into a 1941\u21922023 milestone run behind a '1941 / 2023' ghost word. The curator quote reuses the portrait-collage with a margin caption. Visit pairs address/hours with the real Map.jpg and a typographic 'Buy tickets' link (no button). Newsletter uses an underline form-field with an inline arrow CTA, and the footer is open slash-nav collage on cream. Every non-hero section stays on primary with no accent to satisfy the single-accent rule; only real brand asset filenames are referenced."
